\SE[0]Ah, it's Rasudan. \.The ultimate goal is to defeat
the Demon Lord here. \!\SE[14](But I haven't made it yet.)

\SE[0]Is it okay to have something like that so close by?
\SE[3]Normally, wouldn't it be located further away...

\SE[0]Intentionally, you know. Intentionally. \SE[0]I

quickly. If you know the goal, your motivation will
increase, right? \SE[18]If there's a boss that you think you
can defeat as you grow stronger.
\SE[12]I see. So that's how it is.
